This is the entire attack menu complex. To add a new menu you would simply add another [code]else if (screen == (number)) { [/code]
statement. Adding new menus is easy and thats all you have to do, if you add the menu thats it, compile, run, and it can be called, no messing around with actionbuttons or finding the right tab, for ease of use. Now we get to what is added to clickingbuttons.

