For those of you who havent really messed around with frame174, here is my method for the item on interface
[code]	public void writeInterfaceItem(int id[]) {
		synchronized(c) {
			c.outStream.createFrameVarSizeWord(53);
			c.outStream.writeWord(8847); // 8847
			c.outStream.writeWord(id.length);
			for (int i = 0; i < id.length; i++) {
				c.outStream.writeByte(1);
				if(id[i] > 0) {
					c.outStream.writeWordBigEndianA(id[i]+1);
				} else {
					c.outStream.writeWordBigEndianA(0);
				}
			}
			c.outStream.endFrameVarSizeWord();   
			c.flushOutStream();
		}
	}[/code]
You can add it to the actual skillinterfaces class just make sure to change c.getPA().writeInterfaceItem(item); to writeInterfaceItem(item)
